name: "Afternoon' 'Blast-off"
description: We are piercing the veil of physics through dimensional art and sonic representations of fractal geometry, and we are observing that different emotional intentions behind these creations make them break the laws of physics we are used to. This piece, for example fills in color where I did not add any, and seems to breathe on its own. We implore you to allow this to be much more than optical illusion, and treat it like the spaceship that it truly is
